    "rationale": "12 of 13 V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is offset by the direct relevance of the single validated condition to the COU and by the strong quantitative output comparison results (all E/uval < 1.96, all percent differences < 10%). The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision for the non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending COU.",
